# Conversation with AIDA

## The Make

<iframe src="YOUR_EMBED_LINK_HERE" width="100%" height="600"></iframe>

## Your Take

In this project, I explored how conversational AI shapes interaction between humans and machines. I experimented with prompts, responses, and the role of AI systems in communication.

This project helped me understand both the strengths and limitations of conversational AI. While AI can simulate discussion and provide information quickly, it also depends heavily on human guidance and critical thinking.

## Ethical Considerations

This project raises ethical questions about trust, bias, and responsibility in AI systems. Users may assume AI is always correct because of how confidently it responds, which makes critical thinking important.

