# Optional Dark Mode CSS

Create:

```text
assets/style.css
```

Paste:

```css
body {
    background-color: #121212;
    color: #f0f0f0;
    font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
    line-height: 1.6;
}

a {
    color: #7cc7ff;
}

a:hover {
    color: #ffffff;
}

img {
    max-width: 100%;
}

iframe {
    border-radius: 10px;
}
```

Then inside your layout or HTML head:

```html
<link rel="stylesheet" href="assets/style.css">
```

